Noteworthy changes in Version 3.1.5 (unreleased)
------------------------------------------------

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
GnuPG:          2.2.10
Kleopatra:      3.1.3
GPA:            0.10.0
GpgOL:          2.3.1
GpgEX:          1.0.6
Kompendium DE:  4.0.1
Compendium EN:  3.0.0
